sections.markdown: # Give me all requests with HTTP 5xx without the 503s. And please ignore all the noisy /health requests that we know that they fail from time to time...

input.value:
fetch spans
| filter NOT(contains(http.target, "health"))
| filter isNotNull(http.status_code)
| fieldsAdd toLong(http.status_code), alias: http.status_code
| filter http.status_code >= 500 AND http.status_code != 503
| summarize count(), alias: cnt, by: {http.target, http.status_code}
| filter cnt > 5
| fieldsAdd targetandcode = concat(http.target, " - ", http.status_code)
| fieldsKeep targetandcode, cnt
| sort cnt desc

| filter contains(exception[exception.message], "Risky")
| summarize count(), by:{bin(start_time, 1m)}

| lookup 
	[
		fetch spans, from:now() - 15m, scanLimitGBytes:1000
		| filter isNotNull(http.url) AND isNotNull(k8s.namespace.name)
		| summarize by:{http.url, k8s.namespace.name, trace.id}, count(), alias:cnt
